The quickest check is to go from V+ of the diode string and see if
continuity to pin 1 of TL851 and pin 5 of SN28784 are less than 5 ohms.

Similarly check from ground of your power connector to pin 3 of TL851
and pin 16 of SN28784 are less than 5 ohms.

Best wishes,

